statements: SELECT * FROM MedicalDeviceData;
SELECT device_id, patient_id, heart_rate FROM MedicalDeviceData WHERE device_type = 'ECG';
SELECT device_id, patient_id, blood_pressure FROM MedicalDeviceData WHERE heart_rate > 100;
SELECT device_id, device_type, created_at FROM MedicalDeviceData ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT patient_id, device_type, heart_rate FROM MedicalDeviceData WHERE blood_pressure LIKE '%/%';
SELECT * FROM MedicalDeviceData WHERE device_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT device_id, patient_id, heart_rate FROM MedicalDeviceData WHERE blood_pressure = '120/80';
SELECT device_id, patient_id, device_type, heart_rate, blood_pressure FROM MedicaljsonData WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_id, COUNT(device_id) AS device_count FROM MedicalDeviceData GROUP BY patient_id ORDER BY device_count DESC;
SELECT device_type, AVG(heart_rate) AS avg_heart_rate FROM MedicalDeviceData GROUP BY device_type HAVING avg_heart_rate > 80;
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE age > 30
SELECT patient_name, gender FROM patients WHERE location='New York'
SELECT * FROM vital_signs WHERE heart_rate > 80 ORDER BY record_id DESC
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients WHERE gender='Male' ORDER BY age ASC
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE location='Los Angeles' AND age BETWEEN 20 AND 40
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY patient_name DESC;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM patients JOIN vital_signs ON patients.patient_id = vital_signs.patient_id WHERE heart_rate > 80;
SELECT AVG(body_temperature) AS avg_temp, MAX(heart_rate) AS max_heart_rate, MIN(age) AS min_age FROM vital_signs JOIN patients ON vital_signs.patient_id = patients.patient_id;
SELECT patient_name, location FROM patients WHERE gender = 'Female' AND age BETWEEN 30 AND 50 ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM patients JOIN vital_signs ON patients.patient_id = vital_signs.patient_id WHERE blood_pressure LIKE '%120%' ORDER BY patient_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Patients;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM Patients ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT patient_name, blood_type FROM Patients WHERE age > 50;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM MedicalDevices ORDER BY device_name ASC;
SELECT patient_name, data_time, heart_rate FROM Patients p JOIN PatientData pd on p.patient_id = pd.patient_id ORDER BY data_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM Patients WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'male';
SELECT * FROM PatientData WHERE heart_rate > 100 AND temperature < 98.6;
SELECT device_name, device_type FROM MedicalDevices ORDER BY device_type;
SELECT patient_name, blood_type FROM Patients WHERE patient_name LIKE '%John%' ORDER BY blood_type;
SELECT * FROM Patients;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM Patients WHERE age > 30;
SELECT device_name, device_type, manufacturer FROM MedicalDevices ORDER BY device_type ASC;
SELECT patient_id, temperature, heart_rate, blood_pressure FROM VitalSigns WHERE heart_rate > 80;
SELECT patient_id, message, alert_timestamp FROM Alerts ORDER BY alert_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM Patients WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT name, age, gender FROM Patients WHERE blood_type = 'O-' AND age BETWEEN 20 AND 40;
SELECT p.name, v.temperature, a.message FROM Patients p INNER JOIN VitalSigns v ON p.patient_id = v.patient_id LEFT JOIN Alerts a ON p.patient_id = a.patient_id;
SELECT device_name, device_type, manufacturer, purchase_date FROM MedicalDevices WHERE device_type LIKE '%monitor%' ORDER BY purchase_date;
SELECT COUNT(patient_id) AS total_patients, MAX(age) AS max_age FROM Patients WHERE gender = 'Male';

SELECT patient_id, heart_rate, temperature FROM patient_data ORDER BY temperature DESC
